Class FileExtensionLanguageReasoner

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Context, Emission, Plugin, ReasonerPlugin, Resolution

    public class FileExtensionLanguageReasoner
extends GuidedReasonerPlugin
    Derives the elementOf-Language relationship for bound entities by the file extension of the binding URI. 

     @FileExtension '.java'
 Java : Langauge
 
 aFile : File
 aFile = '/path/to/some/java/file.java'
    Author:
    maxmeffert
